Files:

1.GPL: GNU General Public Licence -- Read Before Making changes and distributing

2.header_struct.h : Header file containing structs for bmp headers.

3.imagedata.h : Header file containing struct for image data.

4.imagefunction.c : Functions for image enhancement/processing:
					a.Convert color image to greyscale image
                                        b.Perform average filtering
                                        c.Perform median filtering

5.imagemain.c : Main Function (program entry point)



Note:

1.The program was developed under GCC using standard ANSI library functions (should be platform independent)

